Package domain

Class User

java.lang.Object
domain.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Subject, Serializable
@Entity public class User extends Object implements Serializable, Subject
Represents a user entity in the system. This class models all user-related data and implements the Subject interface for observer pattern support.
